== Changelog ==
= 1.5.4 =
* Stylistic fixes
* Fixed basic captions when gallery titles are longer than one line
* Updated Galleria JavaScript to non-alpha version

= 1.5.3 =
* Fixed Gallery page template to never show passworded or private galleries

= 1.5.2 =
* Fixed center-aligned images in full-width template

= 1.5.1 =
* Removed stats code option

= 1.5 =
* Added small tag styling
* Added edit links to pages for admins
* Removed title from links on Gallery pages
* Added an image size for galleries to decrease load times

= 1.4.2 =
* Fixed bug with social icon display

= 1.4.1 =
* Fixed styling for long titles on fancy captions
* Added Google+ icon
* Fixed bug preventing image box shadows from being removed

= 1.4 =
* Added ability to create multiple Gallery pages using the [gallery] shortcode
* Added option to control captions on Gallery pages
* Fixed image caption styles
* Added keyboard navigation to single galleries
* Fixed image stretching in old versions of Internet Explorer
* Added dl and table styles

= 1.3.3 =
* Fixed some bugs in the attachment template

= 1.3.2 =
* Removed some duplicate code regarding post types
* Moved Flickr initialization into constructor, for easier child theme overriding
* Added attachment template for posts
* Fixed light color scheme search box display
* Fixed header spacing for a wide logo image

= 1.3.1 =
* Fixed images being squished on the full-width page template

= 1.3 =
* Fixed maximum widths for images & other media
* Changed admin styles to match WordPress defaults
* Accessibility improvements on search form
* Fixed post title tags to allow HTML
* Fixed thumbnail size for gallery pages
* Updated Galleria script to 1.2.5a3
* Fixed IE9 thumbnail issues

= 1.2 =
* Replaced the old logo uploader with a faster version that uses WP core.
* Update Galleria to the latest code. Fixes problems with Opera 11 and IE9.
* Fixed underline styling on post title when using the light color scheme.
* Add the category taxonomy to the gallery post type. This allows users to create custom gallery pages using categories.